      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car has seen plenty of life and is ready for a dedicated new owner to give it some much-needed TLC! While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a fantastic foundation for anyone who loves a hands-on restoration. It's an honest fixer-upper with great potential for the right person!",
