    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that's as reliable as your favorite pair of jeans? This car has been such a joy to own and is totally ready for its next big adventure! It\u2019s in great shape, drives like a dream, and has been super well-cared for over the years. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to take it out on the road. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019re going to love how it feels!",
