      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and recent valve lash adjustment. The suspension geometry remains precise thanks to refreshed polyurethane bushings and updated dampers. While it shows honest patina consistent with its driver-grade status, the drivetrain is robust, providing linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A turn-key performance icon for the technical purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
